---
export const prerender = true;
---
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Persona: The Power User | Admin</title>
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" />
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: Inter, system-ui, sans-serif; min-height: 100vh; background: #030712; color: #f9fafb; }
    .header { background: #111827; border-bottom: 1px solid #1f2937; padding: 16px 24px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
    .logo { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fbbf24, #d97706); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
    .back-link { color: #9ca3af; text-decoration: none; font-size: 13px; padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid #374151; }
    .back-link:hover { color: #fbbf24; border-color: #fbbf24; }
    .container { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 32px 24px; }
    .hero { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 32px; padding: 24px; background: #111827; border-radius: 16px; border: 1px solid #1f2937; border-top: 3px solid #f59e0b; }
    .hero-icon { font-size: 56px; }
    .hero-name { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; }
    .hero-role { font-size: 13px; color: #f59e0b; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
    .section { background: #111827; border: 1px solid #1f2937; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .section-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #fbbf24; margin-bottom: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
    .section p, .section li { font-size: 14px; color: #d1d5db; line-height: 1.7; }
    .section ul { padding-left: 20px; }
    .section li { margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .tag { display: inline-block; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 100px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; background: #451a03; color: #fbbf24; margin: 2px 4px 2px 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <div class="logo">⚙️ xConvert24 Admin</div>
    <a href="/admin/personas" class="back-link">← All Personas</a>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero">
      <div class="hero-icon">⚡</div>
      <div>
        <div class="hero-name">The Power User</div>
        <div class="hero-role">High-Engagement Champion</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">📋 Bio</div>
      <p>The Power User is xConvert24's most engaged persona. They visit daily, maintain long streaks, use multiple converters per session, actively report bugs, suggest features, vote on community items, and chase ConvertCoins milestones. They're the 5% of users who generate 30% of the traffic.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">🎯 Goals</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Maintain daily streak and level up their ConvertCoins balance</li>
        <li>Discover and try every new converter or tool added</li>
        <li>Influence the product roadmap through bug reports and feature suggestions</li>
        <li>Track crypto portfolios, use finance calculators regularly</li>
        <li>Be recognised as a top contributor in the community</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">😤 Pain Points</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Feels unrewarded when there are no new features to explore</li>
        <li>Frustrated when reported bugs aren't fixed quickly</li>
        <li>Wants more granular streak/achievement tracking</li>
        <li>Needs keyboard shortcuts for rapid conversions</li>
        <li>Wants to export conversion history</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">🧭 Typical Journey</div>
      <p>Opens xConvert24 daily (often as a browser start page) → checks coin balance → performs 3+ conversions across categories → checks crypto prices → votes on a bug or suggestion → reads latest blog post → logs out satisfied with streak maintained.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">📊 Key Metrics</div>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Visit frequency:</strong> Daily (7/7 days)</li>
        <li><strong>Session duration:</strong> 5–15 minutes</li>
        <li><strong>Pages per session:</strong> 6–12</li>
        <li><strong>ConvertCoins level:</strong> 5+ (top 2% of users)</li>
        <li><strong>Bug reports submitted:</strong> 3+ per month</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">🏷️ Tags</div>
      <span class="tag">Daily Active</span>
      <span class="tag">Streak Builder</span>
      <span class="tag">Bug Reporter</span>
      <span class="tag">Feature Requester</span>
      <span class="tag">Community Champion</span>
      <span class="tag">Multi-tool User</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
